  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>An continental buffet breakfast is served each morning with freshly baked breads, cakes and pastries. Cereals, yogurts, toast and cold meats and cheeses. </p>
<p>Each evening, a three course dinner is served from the fantastic a la carte menu which is can be taken out on the hotel's restaurant terrace as well as the cosy and traditional indoor dining room. The menu changes frequently and consists of delicious traditional plates such as cured meats, beans, fish fresh from the waters of Lake Garda and homemade pastas. </p>
<p> </p>]]></cateringDescription>
