  <deactivateThisPage>1</deactivateThisPage>
  <description><![CDATA[<p>Just 100 meters from the ferry port and overlooking <a data-udi="umb://document/8bac09b5ee37405a9498e1494235fa01" href="/{localLink:umb://document/8bac09b5ee37405a9498e1494235fa01}" title="Riva">Riva's</a> main square and affluent harbour, the Hotel Centrale boasts one of the most enviable locations in the entire resort. The hustle and bustle of the shopping lanes and quaint cafes sits just a stones' throw from the hotel and the bus station and ferry terminal on your doorstep make it easy to get out and about.</p>
<p>Rooms are comfortable and simple, yet provide everything you need for a comfortable stay. Evening meals for our guests on half board offer a chance to dine from the a la carte menu which sports regional favourites such as spaghetti vongole and scallops with fresh chili and lemon oil. All of these and more can be enjoyed on the al fresco terrace with spectacular views of the surrounding mountains and lake.</p>
<p>Transfer time: approx. 1 hour 45 mins by coach from Verona airport.</p>]]></description>
