  <facilityDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Restaurant</span></strong></p>
<p>Hotel Centrale is home to a wonderful restaurant with a large dining room which spills out onto a sun soaked terrace overlooking the lake. Evening meals consist of three courses which can selected from the a la carte menu where you can find traditional dishes such as slow cooked cured meats, homemade pastas and of course fish caught fresh from the waters of Lake Garda. </p>]]></facilityDescription>
